  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Enhancing Immediate Reintegration Capacity for Burundian Returnees through Housing, Land, Property (HLP), Shelter, Water, Sanitation and Hygiene (WASH) in Burundi</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Through this project, IOM is supporting Burundian returnees from the United Republic of Tanzania through reintegration projects including water, sanitation and hygiene, housing land and property and shelter interventions. A community-based approach, including cash-based interventions is being used based on needs assessments.</narrative>
  </description>
